      <title>墨西哥将停止部分石油出口，挤压全球市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/mexico-to-halt-some-oil-exports-further-squeezing-global-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥国有石油公司计划在未来几个月内停止部分原油出口，此举将减少全球市场紧缩带来的供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/mexico-to-halt-some-oil-exports-further-squeezing-global-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 18:16:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国数据导致日元走弱，日本外汇干预风险上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/yen-weakens-on-us-data-raising-risk-of-japanese-fx-intervention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日元兑美元汇率正在跌向 152 日元，这是交易员认为日本官员干预市场的风险上升的关键水平，因为强劲的美国工厂数据提振了美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/yen-weakens-on-us-data-raising-risk-of-japanese-fx-intervention</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 16:44:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安德烈蒂的 SPAC 交易带来的现金微乎其微，股价暴跌 58%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/andretti-s-ai-spac-deal-brings-little-cash-as-shares-tumble-54</link>
      <description><![CDATA[人工智能初创公司 ZapataComputingHoldingsInc. 与前印地赛车车手迈克尔·安德雷蒂 (Michael Andretti) 的空白支票公司合并后，尽管绝大多数公众投资者对这笔交易持放弃态度，但该公司首次上市后股价暴跌 58%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/andretti-s-ai-spac-deal-brings-little-cash-as-shares-tumble-54</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 16:21:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国数据显示，由于流动性稀薄，新兴市场资产小幅走低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/emerging-assets-edge-lower-amid-thin-liquidity-us-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新兴市场股市和货币周一收低，此前美国最新工厂数据导致交易员重新评估对全球最大经济体降息的押注，打压风险偏好。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-01/emerging-assets-edge-lower-amid-thin-liquidity-us-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 01 Apr 2024 14:12:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着美联储削减赌注的消退，股市与债券一起下跌：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/asian-stocks-set-to-gain-as-fed-awaits-more-data-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[坚实的美国工厂数据强化了美联储将不急于降息的猜测，华尔街交易员导致股票和债券双双走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-31/asian-stocks-set-to-gain-as-fed-awaits-more-data-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 31 Mar 2024 22:04:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
